# Peanut Butter & Jelly Sandwich Recipe

## Ingredients
- 2 slices of bread
- 2 tablespoons peanut butter
- 2 tablespoons jelly or jam (your choice)

## Instructions
1. Spread peanut butter on one slice of bread.
2. Spread jelly or jam on the other slice.
3. Press the two slices together.
4. Cut the sandwich in half if desired.
5. Enjoy!
